      <title>搭建真分布式Hadoop集群指南</title>
      <link>http://xpgreat.com/p/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E7%9C%9F%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E5%BC%8Fhadoop%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/</link>
